									<span class="bg"></span>
									<span class="activity-date">
										<span class="day">10</span>
										<span class="month-year">2月 2026</span>
									</span>
									<span class="activity-title">2025-2026大埔區好學生獎勵計劃頒獎典禮</span>
									<span class="activity-content ellipsis" data-height="180">本校突出表現學生大獎得主為: 5C吳馗生&nbsp;, 5C鄧灝晴&nbsp;, 5D周文星。恭喜以上得獎同學。

</span>
									<span class="details">詳情</span>
								</span>
